# LDM College ERP — Implementation Plan

## Hosting Environment: Hostinger Premium (Shared)

### Constraints
| Restriction | Status | Solution |
|-------------|--------|----------|
| No background workers | ✅ | All operations are request-driven |
| No WebSockets | ✅ | Standard HTTP request/response only |
| No Docker/Node | ✅ | PHP + MySQL only |
| No daemons | ✅ | File-based caching, no Redis |
| Limited file writes | ✅ | Writes only to `public/uploads/` and `api/.cache/` |

### Shared Hosting Safe Features
- **Cache**: File-based in `api/.cache/` with .htaccess protection
- **Uploads**: `public/uploads/gallery/` with subdirectories
- **Logs**: Database-based audit logs, no file logs
- **Sessions**: PHP native sessions (cookie-based)

