## Deployment Checklist

### Pre-Deployment
- [ ] Update `.htaccess` CORS origin to `https://ldmcollege.com`
- [ ] Set JWT secret in production
- [ ] Configure DB credentials
- [ ] Build frontend: `npm run build`

### Hostinger Setup
```bash
# Upload these directories:
/api/           → /public_html/api/
/frontend/dist/ → /public_html/

# Ensure writable:
chmod 755 /public_html/api/.cache/
chmod 755 /public_html/uploads/gallery/
```

### Database
- Import `gibbon_ldm_local` to production
- Update `api/index.php` with production credentials

